# Municipal Issue Reporting API Test File
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or any HTTP client

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Get All Reports
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reports

### Get Reports with Filter
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reports?status=pending

### Create New Report
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Broken Street Light",
  "description": "Street light not working on Main Road",
  "category": "Electricity",
  "location": {
    "address": "Main Road, Ranchi",
    "latitude": 23.3441,
    "longitude": 85.3096
  }
}

### Update Report Status
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in-progress"
}

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users

### Get Global Stats
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stats/global

### Register New User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "citizen"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### AI Vision Health Check
GET http://localhost:5007/health

### Speech Recognition Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health